channel.title: Hello, just need a little help
channel.description:
Hello, i am trying to set up my first rsps and im have a problem that is probably really stupid but i hope i can get some help.. So I downloaded TrisidiaX V3 Final Release and i port forwarded i checked it and im running DUC and i think i got everything i need for it. i changed the compile.bat to my version of java and i did this for environmental variables.. but when i try to run the server it says "Error: could not find or load main class Dexter" but when i checked it is in the folder so idk what to do..
im not closed minded on dling another server if you think this is just a bad server i just want a oldish rsps like 317 economy based for me and my friends to play on
Skype name: CraftableDan
thanks for the help :)
